Li</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140154806441728"><h3 class="no_margin">Aaron T. Fleischauer</h3><p>  <sup>3</sup>  Division of Emerging Infections and Surveillance Services, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, Atlanta, Georgia, United States of America,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Fleischauer%20AT%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20668535">Aaron T. Fleischauer</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140154806439360"><h3 class="no_margin">Xuesen Xing</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup>  Hubei Center for Disease Control and Prevention, Hubei, People\'s Republic of China,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Xing%20X%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20668535">Xuesen Xing</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140154806436992"><h3 class="no_margin">Xiaoqing Jiang</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup>  Hubei Center for Disease Control and Prevention, Hubei, People\'s Republic of China,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Jiang%20X%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20668535">Xiaoqing Jiang</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140154844267424"><h3 class="no_margin">Hongjie Yu</h3><p>  <sup>4</sup>  Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention, Beijing, People\'s Republic of China,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Yu%20H%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20668535">Hongjie Yu</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140154844265056"><h3 class="no_margin">Sonja J. Olsen</h3><p>  <sup>3</sup>  Division of Emerging Infections and Surveillance Services, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, Atlanta, Georgia, United States of America,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Olsen%20SJ%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20668535">Sonja J. Olsen</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140154844262688"><h3 class="no_margin">Adam L. Cohen</h3><p>  <sup>2</sup>  Respiratory Diseases Branch, Division of Bacterial Diseases, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, Atlanta, Georgia, United States of 